{"tid":346101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗 劉灝然先生 翻版金正恩話俾大家知佢係老婆奴...","createTime":"2017-08-03T15:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T23:25:54.000Z","uid":130495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0b8a86243f9b594399a679ea4a71fbb251fb96","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的...我本身同佢係同一間運輸公司係同事...大家都係揸貨VAN...<br />\n<br />\n點知有人持住有老闆撐就日日狗吠屌人老母...日日做金手指搏上位...<br />\n<br />\n我俾佢屌足一個月之後...因為全公司無人反抗佢...我睇唔過眼同佢嘈...<br />\n<br />\n之後佢係電話恐嚇我話見一鑊打我一鑊...又話佢呀叔係大棠村長...<br />\n<br />\n以後唔撚俾我係元朗行街...又搵埋佢個黑社會親生細佬約我講數...<br />\n<br />\n我果日驚到即刻去左元朗警署報警同立即辭職放返低部車係公司...<br />\n<br />\n之後佢同老闆講搞到咁大鑊覺得影響左公司唔好意思就自己辭職...<br />\n<br />\n你老婆有情緒病搵你發洩大撚哂呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死肥仔 我屌你老母呀 又唔知自己幾撚矮 人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿...你一係就帶佢去睇下醫生...一係你收左工走去元朗叫雞...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ro3zl5w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ro3zl5w&h=75e2d7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p1rbjmna\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp1rbjmna&h=ff5aa3f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/byz417ot\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbyz417ot&h=7a5cd935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我想同你講聲...周圍同人講你係葵涌D凍倉等見我有撚用咩...<br />\n<br />\n我係貨櫃碼頭等緊你呀...等我盤左條老命同你盡地一煲...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c2086cf38b171c73bec9c322436159cef0fb4fb3","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d69e79bb105d23dd22fff18dd5756049c023d6","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f9e7cecfb03592e9ba633acc4527a5e74ab539","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b74237a6258cd49b0f900a968273eb056331d2","tid":346101,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01f0f76b6851e4feb1fd6ecf02cb9b60404133d8","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>看圖作文？</blockquote><br />\n我賢仔講大話我仆街死呀"},{"pid":"be6c8b4602c492f0ddce433ab866dc60ec2a5eac","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4b58f962185b0c8d09950bd945623d4f951087","tid":346101,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dac66c219c88f5a41d9b82ac2709f7af47bb361a","tid":346101,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>看圖作文？</blockquote><br />\n我賢仔講大話我仆街死呀</block